**DEADLINE EXTENDED UNTIL NOVEMBER 5 @ 11:59PM**

Engineering Student Services is pleased to present the Fall Undergraduate Research Poster Session

Date: Tuesday, November 17 2020
Time: 4-5:30PM PST
Location:  Zoom!

 

This is a great opportunity for undergraduate students (ranging from freshmen to seniors) to present their recent research on a wide range of projects across the College of Engineering. Participation in the poster session can be included on your resume and applications for graduate school.

How to Apply: The poster session is open to all College of Engineering undergraduate students (including L&S Computer Science) interested in presenting a poster of their research. Research can be from labs at Berkeley or other organizations, including summer REU programs. Please submit an abstract to be included in this event. 

https://forms.gle/E8AfBwqiHpL4AHqy9

If you have questions please contact Nicole McIntyre at nicolemcintyre@berkeley.edu
history.subject: Deadline Extended: Fall 2020 Virtual Undergraduate Research Poster Session
